      ('SUNNY', 'Sunny Aggregator', 'SUNNY/USDT', '4X', 'Sunny is a composable DeFi yield aggregator powered by Solana. The Sunny Governance Token ($SUNNY) will be used to make decisions about the future of the protocol.', 19884700000),
